{"tid":367081,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"決意離開高登，這是我在這裡出的最後一個POST","createTime":"2017-08-20T13:17:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-20T15:03:22.000Z","uid":36497,"like":4,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"59ff2e0436021b6dc650396a09a37c025108fd0a","tid":367081,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:17:23.000Z","msg":"這裏的人學識都很高 <br />\n<br />\n從這裏的人的留言中學會了很多知識 <br />\n<br />\n天文, 地理, 氣象, 歷史, 政治 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這是我一上網就立刻到這裏的原因 <br />\n<br />\n正正是因為我自己都是一個愛好知識的人 <br />\n<br />\n加上這裏的人都多廿靚三十歲的, 同我相若, 岩傾 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我在這裡出了很多很多post, 但99%都是所謂的 &quot;假膠post&quot;, 即是完完全全亂up老作搏大家一笑, <br />\n<br />\n帖內的內容和自己的事完全沒關, 無論出post同reply都係, 甚至好多時同真實既自己係相反 <br />\n<br />\n明明是反雲，卻經常吹奏雲加<br />\n<br />\n明明自己都係支持民主, 卻經常出post罵支持民主人士<br />\n<br />\n明明自己都是90後，卻經常吊鳩90後<br />\n<br />\n歸根究抵都係純粹因為工作時無聊, 所以無無聊聊地出個post <br />\n<br />\n講無聊野 <br />\n<br />\n然後一邊工作, 一邊睇回覆, 自娛一下 <br />\n<br />\n這件事對不喜歡現在的工作的我十分重要 <br />\n<br />\n同時, 我故意講相反野, 因為驚俾人知我既真正身份 <br />\n<br />\n一個知...就會話俾另一個知, 然後一傳十, 十傳百, 就不好了, 我完全唔想俾人知我o係網上既身份, 講過 d 乜 <br />\n<br />\n俾人知道, 我o係呢度暢所欲言, 說傻話, 減減壓的空間就完全被破壞了... <br />\n(雖然我出既post都同自己做過既野無關) <br />\n<br />\n不過, 有一日我忽然發現自己沉迷了這裡....荒廢正業 <br />\n<br />\n離開, 因為不想再在這裏浪費時間了, 往後我還有很多計劃, 操番好體能, 籌備上青山, 練番水, 練好 d 壁球, 鋼琴要考演奏級, 練好渣車, 重投放下了一年多的義工活動, 抽多 d 時間陪女朋友 睇精神科醫生..etc etc <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再見了, 高登各位高學識既人. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b94c7194bb4044d5208c8f64fc98c2359bbbf0a","tid":367081,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e25eb98d614c7222c8eb795dcc8f34f540f23279","tid":367081,"uid":38957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"挽留"},{"pid":"2cb9309b951b6021df98a05b1d81adb4c1564d98","tid":367081,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"冇左豬腦蛇<br />\n以後冇榮華食啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9636c24efb622af40380b1ce121479036cc0e4a4","tid":367081,"uid":43718,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"你都無女"},{"pid":"7dd1683339dd6f69b735499798c13eb5fb144ed3","tid":367081,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:23:21.000Z","msg":"過埋中秋先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3b2a6aeb90425c728e4ca924362148e80d5699","tid":367081,"uid":3122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:23:42.000Z","msg":"上黎緊係9UP當"},{"pid":"d5b37a4527d6e166c28cffb2997b0f4d94352a34","tid":367081,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:24:30.000Z","msg":"你離開高登關連登乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a576d3057df536a6ecd3749702872c615d6ea758","tid":367081,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:28:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都無女</blockquote><br />\n唔好以己度人"},{"pid":"c468fb73ab350f7240343fcbd026874d35bc097e","tid":367081,"uid":9602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d2fdd5d6517731a9b262fed22a6247c4ba65f80","tid":367081,"uid":894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:30:38.000Z","msg":"玩留"},{"pid":"9bd57fb1b81bcad926ebcba55dd67624ba00057b","tid":367081,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-20T13:32:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你都無女</blockquote><br />\n唔好以己度人</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\